# Ignore everything by default; un-ignore only what this repo versions.
# Intentionally NOT listing excluded work/skill names — naming them in a
# public file would itself leak internal tooling info. The repo lives in
# its own folder, so anything we don't cp in simply isn't here.
*

!.gitignore
!README.md
!LICENSE

!skills/
!skills/**
!agents/
!agents/**
!rules/
!rules/**

**/.DS_Store
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
